  "title": "Chief Finance Officer",
  "description": "<p><strong>Position: Chief Financial Officer (CFO)</strong></p><p><strong>Location:</strong> Singapore (frequent overseas travel required)</p><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Lead end-to-end finance functions including reporting, controls, and strategic planning</p></li><li><p>Drive and support <strong>US listing activities</strong>, preferably via <strong>SPAC</strong> (IPO experience also considered)</p></li><li><p>Manage investor relations, auditors, advisors, and regulatory requirements</p></li><li><p>Partner closely with senior management to support rapid business growth and expansion</p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Proven <strong>US listing experience</strong> (SPAC strongly preferred)</p></li><li><p>Strong command of <strong>English and Mandarin</strong> (spoken and written)</p></li><li><p>Strategic yet hands-on finance leader with multinational exposure</p></li><li><p>Singapore-based or willing to relocate; open to frequent travel</p></li></ul>",
